msgid "I think I'll just do it later."
msgstr "また後にしよう。"

msgid "That was easy."
msgstr "簡単だった。"

msgid "This isn't the right classroom for that."
msgstr "それをするのはこの教室ではない。"

msgid "The path is already drawn."
msgstr "道は既に描いてある。"

msgid "Not yet. I'd rather make sure I have everything I need first."
msgstr "まだダメ。先に必要なものを揃えておきたい。"

msgid "Not yet. I want to finish preparing the classrooms first."
msgstr "まだダメ。先に教室の準備をしておきたい。"

msgid "There's some chalk here."
msgstr "チョークがある。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_chalk_get.choice"
msgid "Take it?"
msgstr "取る？"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_chalk_get.choice.Take it?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "取る"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_chalk_get.choice.Take it?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "取らない"

msgid "I'd rather not get into anymore trouble than I already am."
msgstr "これ以上問題を起こすのは控えたい。"

msgid "This is my desk. I keep all kinds of cool stuff here."
msgstr "私の机。色んなカッコいいものが入ってる。"

msgid "This might be useful."
msgstr "これは役に立つかも。"

msgid "Take Dusty Hairpin?"
msgstr "くすんだヘアピンを取る？"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_hairpin_get.choice.Take Dusty Hairpin?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "取る"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_hairpin_get.choice.Take Dusty Hairpin?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "取らない"

msgid "There's nothing else of use for today."
msgstr "他に今日役に立つものはもうない。"

msgid "My desk. I don't need anything from it right now."
msgstr "私の机。いま特に必要なものは入ってない。"

msgid "Burning the school down is not part of the ritual."
msgstr "儀式の手順には学校への放火は含まれていない。"

msgid "There's a pair of scissors here."
msgstr "ハサミがある。"

msgid "Take Scissors?"
msgstr "ハサミを取る？"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_scissors.choice.Take Scissors?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "取る"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_scissors.choice.Take Scissors?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "取らない"

msgid "It's already done."
msgstr "もう揃えてある。"

msgid "This isn't the time for that."
msgstr "今はそんなことをしている場合ではない。"

msgid "Return scissors?"
msgstr "ハサミを戻す？"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_scissors_on_shelf.choice.Return scissors?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "戻す"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.item_scissors_on_shelf.choice.Return scissors?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "戻さない"

msgid "Some geometry books."
msgstr "幾何学の教科書数冊。"

msgid "A clean chalkboard."
msgstr "きれいな黒板。"

msgid "A wooden desk."
msgstr "木の机。"

msgid "A paper slip with rules for students."
msgstr "校則の書かれた紙。"

msgid "There's no time for rules right now."
msgstr "今は校則を守ってる時間はない。"

msgid "Some classroom attendance sheets and schedules."
msgstr "出欠表とスケジュール表。"

msgid "A happy green plant."
msgstr "楽しげな観葉植物。"

msgid "The plant is no longer happy."
msgstr "観葉植物。もう楽しげじゃない。"

msgid "The teacher's podium."
msgstr "教壇。"

msgid "Some boring textbooks."
msgstr "退屈な教科書が数冊。"

msgid "Some very thick, school-related books."
msgstr "分厚い学校関連の本が数冊。"

msgid "Some books and... chalk."
msgstr "本が数冊と……チョーク。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.misc_shelf2b.choice"
msgid "Take it?"
msgstr "取る？"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.misc_shelf2b.choice.Take it?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "取る"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.misc_shelf2b.choice.Take it?"
msgid "No"
msgstr "取らない"

msgid "There's nothing else of use."
msgstr "他に使えるものはない。"

msgid "A simple trash can. Its contents look trashy."
msgstr "シンプルなゴミ箱。中身はいかにもゴミという感じだ。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.misc_window1.dlg.narrator"
msgid "The curtains should stay closed."
msgstr "カーテンは閉めたままにしておかないといけない。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.misc_window2.dlg.narrator"
msgid "The curtains should stay closed."
msgstr "カーテンは閉めたままにしておかないといけない。"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.misc_window3.dlg.narrator"
msgid "The curtains should stay closed."
msgstr "カーテンは閉めたままにしておかないといけない。"

msgid "Should I sort the desks in this classroom now?"
msgstr "今この教室の机を揃える？"

msgctxt "events.Prologue_Classroom_1.move_enter.choice.Should I sort the desks in this classroom now?"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "揃える"

msgid "Not yet"
msgstr "まだやめておく"

msgid "This should be easy."
msgstr "これは簡単ね。"
